# Environment Configuration
# ========================
# This project uses separate environment files for DEV and PROD:
#
#   .env.development  → Loaded by `npm run dev` (local development)
#   .env.production   → Loaded by `npm run build` (production builds)
#
# Setup:
#   1. Copy .env.development.example to .env.development
#   2. Copy .env.production.example to .env.production
#   3. Fill in the ANON_KEY values from Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
